    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Calling all weekend warriors and restoration fans! This vehicle is the ultimate blank canvas for someone looking for a rewarding project. While it currently needs significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a fantastic opportunity to roll up your sleeves and bring a classic back to life. If you're looking for a budget-friendly entry into your next big build, this is the one for you!",
